{"id":"10707373-008e-4fa5-8daf-a2648c72c53c","name":"Youmu Konpaku","description":"<h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 223, 226)\">«If there is something I can't make clear, I try cutting it!»</span></h4><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Youmu Konpaku (or Myon), character of the Touhou Project game series by ZUN. A fairly popular character in the franchise, who has appeared in games as a playable character on multiple occasions.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Youmu is a gardener and swordsmanship instructor in Hakugyokurou in Netherworld. She serves Yuyuko Saigyouji. Youmu is half-human, half-phantom. Being straight forward and earnest, Youmu tends to get picked on a lot, but it doesn't seem to bother her much...</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\">Additional images:</h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 609px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_789569f3-6795-4e2e-b50c-3998f8823f71.webp?width=1000\">Art by<a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/artists/158949\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Azure Silan</strong></a> <strong>🠕</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_4674e8f8-4270-4052-8174-f59bd3c0ef88.webp?width=1000\">Art by<strong> </strong><a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/artists/250828\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Youmu-Kun</strong></a> <strong>🠕</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_9e4f0b61-166d-4d28-b957-db35784d57e1.webp?width=1000\">Art by<strong> </strong><a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/artists/250828\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Youmu-Kun</strong></a> <strong>🠕</strong></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjZ4dbX8OGIAxVqxQIHHdFKAJUQFnoECBUQAQ&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsmm-e.ru%2Farticles%2F-pystoi-nevidimyi-simvol-dlya-vk-instagram-drygih-socsetei-i-nikov-html-1642833000%2F&amp;usg=AOvVaw13K4qjmlvBGevzpSzaEHHF&amp;opi=89978449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ㅤ</a></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\">- Author's Note -</h3><p>Another Touhou bot! <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">(I haven't forgotten about Neptunia, no)</mark>. Youmu is probably one of my favorite characters <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">(we don't pay attention to the fact that I haven't played Touhou, still)</mark>, so I hope I didn't screw it up. As always, I didn't add a spell-cards system because I thought it would be weird to rp this with a bot, but other than that I tried to make it as canon as possible, so... Enjoy the bot, as always!</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"593a9893-0c98-45ac-977f-199116f88f18_96679ba3-4d7c-450f-ba88-08a32088f0f3.webp","creator":"Io711","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","🙇 Submissive","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3073,"messages":85528,"created_at":"2024-11-07T01:22:35.645167+00:00"}